Red Bull Shay’ imoto: Come witness twelve of South Africa’s high-profile spinners go head-to-head in a battle toward winning the first Red Bull Shay’ Imoto championship crown. Details: The event takes place on October 19 at Wheelz N Smoke, Kliprivier Drive, Johannesburg South.
